data.description: 9 Tillinghast is exactly what you've been looking for! An investors dream to own a property that hosts 3 spacious, vacant units (3/1, 3/1, 2/1) in the Upper Clinton Hill section of Newark. See the 3-car detached garage placed in a big lot tucked behind the spacious shared driveway. This property has separate utilities in a large full basement with a separate entrance and egress windows. This is your opportunity to generate significant rental income! Located in a high demand area near popular shopping centers, eateries, and general entertainment. 45 minute commute to NYC. Being sold strictly AS-IS.
